    "body": "Yeah I've been running into this too.  The standard workaround is to increase the limit on the number of file descriptors, but I would prefer to put in a solution that didn't require that.\n\nIssue #7772 is most likely the issue that @alexcrichton was thinking of.  (Its closed, but I'm not quite clear on whether it was closed because the bots had their file limits increased, _or_ if the increase in the limits is masking the fact that this bug persists.)_\n",
