    "body": "Ah yes, that was indeed the issue I was thinking of. It appears that the `libstd` tests automatically increase the file descriptor limit, but this is just affecting `compiletest` now because it's got so many children.\n\nI think the fix here is to call `raise_fd_limit` in `compiletest` on osx. Doing it in a non-hacky way could get interesting though.\n",
